<p><br /></p>

<p>The article provides an overview of the ADE mechanism and a literature review of developments since its introduction a decade ago.
Currently, there are 44 ADEs supporting a wide range of applications, but also application-agnostic purposes such as harmonisation with national geographic information standards.</p>

